snippet.textDisplay:
My favorite features of this masterpiece:

Akbar Ali (The sublime voice)
Javed Bashir (The passionate voice)
Amir Zaki (Scintillating solo)
Ahad Kayani (Kickass Drumming)
All guitarists (great riffs and rhythm)
Gul (Sarangi player. Stimulating solos)
The violin uncle and friends (The story tellers)
Mannu (the groove master, the unsung hero of every CS song ever)
Babar Khanna (the beat master)
Jaffer Zaidi (The orchestrator of this genius)

Mann atkiya is gaane de naal
